						               													<description>The Murder Management Card Game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A horror-themed world where YOU play as the killers. Bid against your opponents to catch, scare, and kill your victims. Become the most lethal lunatic around!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You start with a killer, a lair, and a 30-card deck filled with various items to catch, scare, and kill your victims. Each player draws 5 cards and turns over 2 victim cards in the center of the table. Each card from the deck has two uses. Either players use their hand to bid on the best victims available to be their target, or they can use them to match a catch, scare, and kill a victim and attempt to end them for good. Each victim has a value of one to five so bid wisely! Already have your two victims? You can spend your money at the creep shop, a deck full of weird item cards and actions to mess with your opponents.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A two-player game can take around 30 minutes, but supports up to five players. The more players in the game, the more victims to bid on. The first player to kill 15-points worth of victims wins the game!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
